text: Dobbins Stadium is a baseball stadium in Davis, California. It is the home field of the UC Davis Aggies baseball team. The stadium holds 3,500 spectators and opened in 1986. ==See also== * List of NCAA Division I baseball venues ==References== ==External links== *Venue information Category:Baseball venues in California Category:University of California, Davis campus Category:College baseball venues in the United States Category:Sports venues in Yolo County, California Category:UC Davis Aggies baseball
